{"tid":1263931,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一位經歷過六四的老師想對你講的話","createTime":"2019-06-28T12:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T00:06:59.000Z","uid":178583,"like":95,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8ec2ece87e93fe8401f29792d541ddf0d1bb28","tid":1263931,"uid":178583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:19:31.000Z","msg":"佢曾經係我老師，但如今已退休，係一個香港市民，佢拜託我係連登上幫佢道出佢對大家既憂慮與關心。<br />\n<br />\n佢講左句說話 「殺君馬者道旁兒」<br />\n呢句說話既典故係咁既：<br />\n有一個人，騎着一匹馬在路上跑。因為馬跑得飛快，不斷有路人為它鼓掌叫好。馬及騎馬的人也很得意。於是快馬加鞭，繼續在驛道上狂奔。跑得越快，叫好的人就越多。跑了幾百里之後，這匹馬突然一個跟頭栽倒，就死了。騎馬的人摔下來，急得想哭「好好的馬，怎麼會死呢？」這時一個老者走過來說：「殺君馬者，道旁兒也。」意思是說，殺你馬的人，就是那些在路旁給你鼓掌叫好的人。<br />\n<br />\n由尋日開始，陸續見到世界各地的報章出現眾籌的文章，其實好感動。香港人的抗爭行動，不斷係度進化，唔再係單單靠遊行。有人話，將香港既事件放到國際平台係唯一既出路。但另一方面，其實亦可能係一條死路。<br />\n<br />\n「係歷史上我地可以睇到，共產黨善於分化、造假，而且從不妥協，如果外國有聲援，可能更加危險。六四個年我同你地一樣都係學生，一樣企出黎支持抗爭，但萬萬估唔到會發生屠殺學生的事件，呢件事至今仍無法釋懷。所以你地<strong>一定唔好太進取</strong>，別讓六四重現！」呢段說話，就係佢想講比你地知既。<br />\n<br />\n有時會覺得，救香港真係好難。呢三個禮拜，真係令我覺得好攰。但由於已經有個post去鼓勵大家，我就唔多講啦。但係，每次令我有動力繼續出去既，係你地，每個一齊捱既香港人！<br />\n<br />\nBe water, it's true. 要醒目地勇武！我就唔講太多啦，希望你地睇完，都可以思考下呢位老師所講既說話。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，繼續加油！"},{"pid":"c59be0fc283a2e8256f43733f5956aa7ffefb60a","tid":1263931,"uid":31215,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"我都有呢個感覺<br />\n過埋G20<br />\n過埋71<br />\n<br />\n一係爭取多少少野<br />\n一係俾人大打一鑊<br />\n一係兩傘重演，熱情不再而潰敗"},{"pid":"52a09905f98d42e3935f0c448f5a163548c5b190","tid":1263931,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:42:14.000Z","msg":"請謹慎小心"},{"pid":"1a274da4c53416f52c2d4807196ec8b73d8bcca9","tid":1263931,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:42:57.000Z","msg":"請謹慎小心"},{"pid":"7f0dcbd99252e10926c0da81cc848bde47ea3deb","tid":1263931,"uid":227942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:46:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"570f8a657406df6c6da70130d5665424f0120be4","tid":1263931,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec5f3cf8b0339863c826492b5b83b034f1f6523b","tid":1263931,"uid":94001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"baf690c8ab67b60c19e8ccbd7c179c06882ba2cb","tid":1263931,"uid":201178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"想同老師講聲多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知老師係之後既方向有冇咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c2912c585a3556ad4b414b26cce2e64cb0205a","tid":1263931,"uid":259156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adc6f29f97269fc0bd4a99cbe94bbf0c1fcb109","tid":1263931,"uid":178228,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CVUpR4LWsAIJIJA?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCVUpR4LWsAIJIJA%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=b3c07ace&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6d1bf8b2ad271f9e410a092279b354b01bc9b9d","tid":1263931,"uid":268592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf690c8ab67b60c19e8ccbd7c179c06882ba2cb","tid":1263931,"uid":201178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"想同老師講聲多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知老師係之後既方向有冇咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"ditto.<br />\n只有邪惡唸唔到的毒招，請多加討論分享經驗同預防。"},{"pid":"fbf3eff8b4cf30a9c59a2ad1a65bf9c2f0ca768f","tid":1263931,"uid":177807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:21:33.000Z","msg":"即使係正氣 如果太強勢<br />\n有些人會選擇不擇手段 企圖勝過你<br />\n勇武者要當心"},{"pid":"e685127d3cd543327a5ef532668f710f0191f720","tid":1263931,"uid":261433,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"七一之後要專注文宣<br />\n<br />\n有啲野岩就岩錯就錯<br />\n<br />\n十年後無人知發生咩事<br />\n<br />\nBut remember remember , the fifth of November"},{"pid":"dc5694a83a3eb904d1daaf3b56599a67fd71b946","tid":1263931,"uid":265829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:33:43.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"ff2ead93d0a2604dfc6e5ca0a9060a1a4b8a6586","tid":1263931,"uid":194718,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:40:46.000Z","msg":"就係中共唔敢六四重現先更加要對住佢大喝一聲<br />\n六四重現就只會加速中共倒台, 血就一定會流, 但唔會白流<br />\n<br />\n呢位經歷過六四的老師心地好, 但太幼稚或和理非, 又想爭取又唔想流血, 咁你想點?"},{"pid":"d5142da6748d6df0c18a781d70630d78e758221f","tid":1263931,"uid":265389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:04:56.000Z","msg":"但中國想收番台灣，香港係個重要既一國兩制既例子。<br />\n<br />\n六四香港人甚至全世界，都記左三十年，一定會記落去。<br />\n<br />\n斷估今次佢唔會血腥鎮壓，唔係既話，統戰部真係再放幾多錢落台灣買人心都收復唔到。（其實卧底民主之母木木正幾時會去抹窗？）<br />\n<br />\n同埋依家全世界睇住香港，出解放軍鎮壓，美國取消香港特別關稅地位，取消聯繫匯率，咁都玩死左人民幣。"},{"pid":"d65943475cfc03202bfee0e54f8c3599b093164a","tid":1263931,"uid":243854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:08:19.000Z","msg":"閣下得一個POST，又叫大家唔好出現六四，又想講唔好落中共面？<br />\n利申：我從不鼓勵人哋勇武，因為後果我幫唔到人承受"},{"pid":"3d80811330c27419b2f890d2f29f06abbbc7c3a6","tid":1263931,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:08:28.000Z","msg":"所以七一和理非更加要多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf197ca648bfe53c11edc53addbc2167b3ef1d0","tid":1263931,"uid":265389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff2ead93d0a2604dfc6e5ca0a9060a1a4b8a6586","tid":1263931,"uid":194718,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:40:46.000Z","msg":"就係中共唔敢六四重現先更加要對住佢大喝一聲<br />\n六四重現就只會加速中共倒台, 血就一定會流, 但唔會白流<br />\n<br />\n呢位經歷過六四的老師心地好, 但太幼稚或和理非, 又想爭取又唔想流血, 咁你想點?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:14:47.000Z","msg":"等我試下翻譯佢既話<br />\n普通上左岸既癈老叫癈青<br />\n<br />\n「世侄，我都後生過，但你要知咩係 得些好意需回手，搞到件事咁大對你冇好處。那，我都經歷過架，你都係早啲番歸抖下啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8406f99dde5e08a230d7375262e55f1345316d4","tid":1263931,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:22:45.000Z","msg":"喂 你老師係咪用錯比喻"},{"pid":"e4f5df4cc940c137d3749f14c1686a525fb055e3","tid":1263931,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:35:19.000Z","msg":"謹慎小心同有戒心<br />\n但同時都要繼續諗點樣可以成效大<br />\n而家去到個位係政府擺明拖<br />\n然後g20後就大反擊係咁拉人"},{"pid":"7341204481185ddb3a984da3dd4304c797343363","tid":1263931,"uid":232407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:36:21.000Z","msg":"明日的世界不屬於過去懦弱的失敗者，上一代安於逸樂苟且偷生，留給下一代爛攤子。你呢個so call老師懺悔了沒有? 有何資格指指點點?"},{"pid":"c9b79eca74d109cfcd2e60f88d54b353885e5b74","tid":1263931,"uid":232407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:40:19.000Z","msg":"請大家善用起底功能<br />\n最近大量新account全面進場<br />\n維穩的手段愈來愈高明"},{"pid":"2b2a4c93108211a0f07e984180df96f01e97fa7e","tid":1263931,"uid":134778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:44:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"272813ab43773c5ef7a4000249a4db818b8b5ce6","tid":1263931,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:06:59.000Z","msg":"push"}]}